539
00:21:20,980 --> 00:21:23,315
(cheering)

540
00:21:23,315 --> 00:21:24,850
That's the spirit, everyone!

541
00:21:24,850 --> 00:21:27,219
Now let's play some Vanguard!

542
00:21:27,219 --> 00:21:29,221
(cheering)

543
00:21:29,221 --> 00:21:33,125
♪

544
00:21:33,125 --> 00:21:34,660
Well, I'm glad
they didn't forfeit

545
00:21:34,660 --> 00:21:36,529
