to learn to stay out

547
00:21:38,397 --> 00:21:39,632
of other people's business.

548
00:21:39,632 --> 00:21:40,900
I couldn't agree more.

549
00:21:40,900 --> 00:21:43,235
Start paying attention to
our team and the games ahead,

550
00:21:43,235 --> 00:21:45,638
or we'll lose our
matches and blame you.

551
00:21:45,638 --> 00:21:47,740
Oh, you're too kind, Yuri.

552
00:21:47,740 --> 00:21:50,242
Now, let's show
those guys who's boss.

553
00:21:50,242 --> 00:21:52,144
(laughing)

554
00:21:53,612 --> 00:22:09,128
♪

555
00:22:09,128 --> 00:22:10,830
Hold on, Kamui.

556
00:22:10,830 --> 00:22:14,266
I know how badly you wanted
to play in this tournament.

557
00:22:14,266 --> 00:22:16,335
That's why I'll do
everything in my power

558
00:22:16,335 --> 00:22:19,738
to get us to the finals.

559
00:22:19,738 --> 00:22:22,741
Your team will be
waiting for you.

560
00:22:26,779 --> 00:23:56,035
♪

561
00:23:59,838 --> 00:24:02,408
♪

562
00:24:02,408 --> 00:24:04,944
What are we gonna
do about Kamui?

563
00:24:04,944 --> 00:24:07,246
Did you forget what
Team Caesar told us?

564
00:24:07,246 --> 00:24:09,148
Oh, yeah, the thing
we should focus on

565
00:24:09,148 --> 00:24:10,616
is making it to the finals,

566
00:24:10,616 --> 00:24:13,352
so let's do our best
to win some matches.

567
00:24:13,352 --> 00:24:15,321
You can count on me.

568
00:24:15,321 --> 00:24:17,523
Thanks, Misaki.

569
00:24:17,523 --> 00:24:20,326
Next time, "Jurassic Army."

570
00:24:20,326 --> 00:24:23,495
I'm imagining myself winning
the first match for my team.

571
00:24:23,495 --> 00:24:25,331
I'm focused, calm, and ready.

572
00:24:25,331 --> 00:24:28,767
Aichi Sendou to the rescue.

